page.title: 11One day in 1985-A.Roythorne
page.content:
{7.40a.m.}Got up and got dressed. {7.55a.m.}Had breakfast(Weetabix and Krispies,toast,cup of tea).{8.10a.m.} Flute practice upstairs.{8.20a.m.} Cleaned my teeth.{8.35a.m.}Tracy called for me and we walked to school together.{8.40a.m.}Arrived at school.{ {9.09a.m.}Maths. work.{10.05a.m.}Went to Melton swimming baths to swim(passed Grade Two){11.05a.m.} English work.{12noon}Went home for dinner today (Fillet of plaice, potatoes, kidney beans, and tomato sauce. For pudding I had semolina pudding and jam. I had a glass of orange to drink).
**The day is continued on page 12**
